name: STARBREEDERS
description:
From a protostar to a yellow dwarf. Red giants, white dwarfs. From a supernova to a neutron star. Black holes and the metaverse.
In the multiverse of realities entities of enormous power are approaching singularity. A collection of 597 STARBREEDERS with 8 rarity traits. Exclusive discord channels for 8 levels of star types hodlers. A community project envisioned to bild a DAO, metaverse experiences and much more. Let's collaborate and explore the multiverse!
